      <scopecontent id="aspace_980c1c576f697b07083a7da2f44ecd96">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This intentionally assembled collection consists of posters and postcards documenting lesbian, gay, transgender, bisexual, and queer student life at Yale, specifically gay pride week events and activities. Also included are posters documenting plays written by William Schwalbe.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
